  <span id="freeText3624868531344933022" style="display:none">This book is so infomative on so many subjects, such as African culture/tribes, FGM, asylum seekers, life in prison, legal matters in the USA. I was really absorbed by it, I think it's very well written and throughout the book I felt myself gaining knowledge, compassion and an increasing feeling that I need and want to help. I would really recommend this to anyone who's looking for a meaningful read!</span>
