<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/3170677-tears-of-the-desert"><img alt="Tears of the Desert: A Memoir of Survival in Darfur" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1320412518l/3170677._SX98_.jpg" />
